# Nimbus pack — layer registry. Read by ./nimbus (and, later, install/revert/update).
# Pipe-delimited; fields are trimmed; lines starting with # and blanks are ignored.
# Columns:  id | dir | sudo | install | revert | title
#   install/revert are the per-layer entrypoints (run from the layer dir);
#   "-" means none (e.g. layer 1 is one-way — no clean revert script).
#
# id | dir                  | sudo | install                    | revert    | title
1    | 1-base               | yes  | nimbus-cachyos-macos.sh -y | -         | macOS desktop base — theme, dock, blur, animations, Spotlight, light/dark toggle
2    | 2-settings-refine    | no   | install.sh                 | revert.sh | Monochrome System Settings icons + NimbusRefined Kvantum fork
3    | 3-krunner-finder     | yes  | install.sh                 | revert.sh | Two-line KRunner rows + Ask-Claude/Hermes/web-search runner
4    | 4-login-lock         | yes  | install.sh                 | revert.sh | Big Sur SDDM login + lock screens
5    | 5-system-qol         | yes  | install.sh -y              | revert.sh | paccache, Flatpak/Flathub, fish tooling, Timeshift
6    | 6-local-ai           | yes  | install.sh -y              | revert.sh | On-GPU Ollama + Hermes/Gemma/Qwen Modelfiles
7    | 7-notifications      | yes  | install.sh -y              | revert.sh | Apple-style swaync toasts + center, scheme-synced
8    | 8-dolphin-quicklook  | no   | install.sh                 | revert.sh | Space previews the selection via kiview (Quick Look)
9    | 9-gpu-effects        | no   | install.sh -y              | revert.sh | Glass blur fork + GLSL shaders + interactive aurora wallpaper
10   | 10-shader-engine     | no   | install.sh                 | revert.sh | Standalone bevy/wgpu GPU fluid engine (Nimbus Flux)
11   | 11-app-unify         | no   | install.sh -y              | revert.sh | Cross-app uniformity — browsers, Electron, Flatpak share the WhiteSur frame/theme
